  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf, \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf \u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0bb5\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf \u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Call for two-wheeler rally in Jharkhand to demand resignation of President, Prime Minister and Govt.",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Some public organizations have called for a two-wheeler rally from Jaffna University towards Jaffna Nagar at 9 am on Saturday (9) to demand the resignation of the President, Prime Minister and the government.",
        "The protest was called at a media conference held at Father Selva Art Gallery, Jaffna.",
        "It is further revealed that this protest was called as a result of a decision reached in a meeting held today on 07th Thursday between the representatives of Jaffna district mass organizations, trade unions, political parties and public organizations.",
        "Jaffna University Teachers Union, Semmugam River Committee, National Council of Arts and Literature, Tamil National Cultural Council, Jaffna District Fishermen's Association, Voice of the Voiceless, Pluralist Democracy Forum, New Democratic Maxis Lenina Party, Mass Organization for Social Justice are supporting the protest, according to the organizers. reported.",
        "On the 9th of July, trade unions, mass organizations and civil organizations have called for a protest across the country, and Jaffna has also been called for a protest.",
        "Saba Thanujan of Mass Organization for Social Justice, Manoranjan, President of Jaffna University Teachers Union, Selvam Kathirkamanathan of New Democratic Marxism Lenina Party, S.Dileepan of Pluralist Democracy Forum participated in this media meeting."
      ],
